{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for lots-- for-- well, for reasons which, which I thought was best.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have a good relationship with their mother to this day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she even felt it would, would be better if there was less disruption to their childhood, if she stayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to Moriah College up the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had rights to come in anytime she wanted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had a very, very easy relationship and even to this day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not saying there isn't any resentment, I'm sure there is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But as far as broken marriages is-- is concerned, it's, it's, it's pretty good.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I married, yes, nearly eight years ago, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gee, I'd better-- I'd better get this right, don't I?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Now you're asking me things which happened only a short time ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the 11th of December, eight years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'87.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Danielle.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grynberg.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She-- she was married before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She married actually-- her first husband was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So-- although she is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She has a stepson-- she has-- I have a stepson, she has a son, who also-- well, nobody's living in the house now.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they all lived-- we all lived together here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trent.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I tried to-- to give them the sort of childhood that I didn't have, obviously.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't succeed, in the sense that I think they were traumatized in a different way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I think that, it doesn't matter whether it's my marriage you're talking about or any marriage in which there is a divorce, it affects, it affects the children.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think that they've come through it fairly well.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
